计算波动方程基本解

关于方向作傅里叶变换
$$
\begin{align*}
\frac{\partial^2\hat{E}(\xi,t)}{\partial t2}+|\xi|2\hat{E}(\xi,t)=\delta(t)
\end{align*}

\begin{align*}
\hat{E}1=\sin(|\xi|t),\quad \hat{E}2=\cos(|\xi|t)
\end{align*}









\begin{align*}
E{+}(x,t) &= F^{-1}(\hat{E}(\xi,t))\
&= (2\pi){-3}\int_{R3}\frac{\sin(|\xi|t)}{|\xi|}e^{i\xi x}d\xi
\end{align*}

\begin{align*}
E{+}(x,t)&=(2\pi){-3}\int_{0}{+\infty}\frac{\sin(\eta t)}{\eta}\eta^2 d\eta\int_{0}{2\pi}d\varphi\int_{0}{\pi}e^{i|x|\eta \cos(\theta)}\sin\theta d\theta\
&=(2\pi){-2}\int_{0}{\infty}\frac{\sin(\eta t)}{|x|}d\eta\int_{-1}^{1}\cos(|x|\eta y)+i\sin(|x|\eta y)d(|x|\eta y)\
&=\frac{2}{4\pi2|x|}\int_{0}{+\infty}\sin(\eta t)\sin(|x|\eta)d\eta\
&=\frac{2}{4\pi2|x|}\cdot\frac{1}{2}\int_{0}{+\infty}\cos((|x|-t)\eta)-\cos((|x|+t)\eta)d\eta\
&=\frac{1}{4\pi^2|x|}\lim\limits_{A\to +\infty}\int_{0}^{A}\cos((|x|-t)\eta)-\cos((|x|+t)\eta)d\eta\
&=\frac{1}{4\pi|x|}\lim\limits_{A\to \infty}\frac{1}{\pi}\Big[\frac{\sin A(|x|-t)}{|x|-t}-\frac{\sin A(|x|+t)}{|x|+t}\Big]\
&=\frac{1}{4\pi|x|}(\delta(|x|-t)-\delta(|x|+t))\
&=\frac{H(t)}{4\pi |x|}\delta(|x|-t)
\end{align*}

能量积分法

下面讨论二维波动方程定解问题的唯一性和稳定性，采用能量法来处理

对于二维的薄膜振动，有

动能为

位能

$$
\begin{align*}
V=\frac{1}{2}\int_{\Omega} T(u_{x}2+u_{y}2)dxdy
\end{align*}
$$

于是，总能量为

$$
\begin{align*}
E(t)=\int_{\Omega}u_{t}2+a2(u_x2+u_y2)dxdy,\quad a^2=\frac{T}{\rho}
\end{align*}
$$

由物理学知道，当薄膜系统不受外力时，即，系统的总能量守恒，即，下面从数学上推导这个等式，即

能量等式

能量等式：当，系统的总能量守恒，即

证明：

$$
\begin{align*}
&\frac{d E(t)}{dt}=\frac{d}{dt}\int_{\Omega}u_{t}2+a2(u_x2+u_y2)dxdy\
=&\int_{\Omega}2u_tu_{tt}+a^2(2u_xu_{xt}+2u_yu_{yt})dxdy
\end{align*}
$$

其中

代入有

$$
\begin{align*}
\frac{d E(t)}{dt}&=2\int_{\Omega}u_{t}u_{tt}+a2(\partial_x(u_xu_t)+\partial_{y}(u_yu_t))-a2u_t(u_{xx}+u_{yy})dxdy\
&=2a^2\int_{\Omega}\partial_x(u_xu_t)+\partial_{y}(u_yu_t)dxdy\
&=2a^2\int_{\partial \Omega}u_xu_t\cos(n,x)+u_yu_t\cos(n,y)dS
\end{align*}
$$

由于，可得，于是

能量不等式

当外力时，对估计，讨论

  • 计算

    $$
    \begin{align*}
    &\frac{d E(t)}{dt}=\frac{d}{dt}\int_{\Omega}u_{t}2+a2(u_x2+u_y2)dxdy\
    =&2\int_{\Omega}u_tu_{tt}+a^2(u_xu_{xt}+u_yu_{yt})dxdy\
    =&2\int_{\Omega}u_{t}u_{tt}+a2(\partial_x(u_xu_t)+\partial_{y}(u_yu_t))-a2u_t(u_{xx}+u_{yy})dxdy\
    =&2\int_{\Omega}u_tfdxdy+2a^2\int_{\Omega}\partial_x(u_xu_t)+\partial_{y}(u_yu_t)dxdy\
    =&2\int_{\Omega}u_tf;dxdy+2a^2\int_{\partial \Omega}u_xu_t\cos(x,n)+u_yu_t\cos(y,n)ds\
    =&2\int_{\Omega}u_tf;dxdy
    \end{align*}
    $$

    即

    $$
    \begin{align*}
    \frac{d E(t)}{dt}=&2\int_{\Omega}u_tf;dxdy\
    \le&\int_{\Omega}u_t2+f2;dxdy\
    \le&\int_{\Omega}u_{t}2+a2(u_x2+u_y2)dxdy+\int_{\Omega}f^2;dxdy\
    =&E(t)+\int_{\Omega}f^2;dxdy
    \end{align*}
    $$

    即有

    两边乘以，得到

    $$
    \begin{align*}
    e^{-t}\frac{d E(t)}{dt}-e^{-t}E(t)\le e{-t}\int_{\Omega}f2;dxdy
    \end{align*}
    $$

    于是

    $$
    \begin{align*}
    \frac{d}{dt}(e^{-t}E(t))\le e{-t}\int_{\Omega}f2;dxdy
    \end{align*}
    $$

    得到

    $$
    \begin{align*}
    e^{-t}E(t)-E(0)\le \int_{0}{t}e{-\tau}\int_{\Omega}f^2(x,y,\tau)dxdyd\tau
    \end{align*}
    $$

    对于，有

    $$
    \begin{align*}
    E(t)\le& e^{t}\Big( E(0)+\int_{0}{t}e{-\tau}\int_{\Omega}f^2(x,y,\tau)dxdyd\tau\Big)\
    \le& C(E(0)+\int_{0}{T}\int_{\Omega}f2(x,y,t)dxdydt)
    \end{align*}
    $$

  • 令

    计算

    从而有

    两边乘以，得到

    于是

    $$
    \begin{align*}
    e^{-t}E_0(t)-E_{0}(0)\le \int_0{\tau}e{-\tau}E(\tau)d\tau
    \end{align*}
    $$

    即

    $$
    \begin{align*}
    E_0(t)\le e{t}\Big(E_0(0)+\int_0{\tau}e^{-\tau}E(\tau)d\tau\Big)
    \end{align*}
    $$

    E_0(t)\le C\Big(E_{0}(0)+E(0)+\int_{0}{T}\int_{\Omega}f2(x,y,t)dxdydt\Big)
    \end{align*}
    $$

二维波动方程柯西问题的唯一性与稳定性

二维波动方程的初值问题

由于此时能量

$$
\begin{align*}
E(t)=\int_{R2}u_t2+a2(u_x2+u_y^2)dxdy
\end{align*}
$$

发散，于是不考虑全局的能量，考虑局部能量的估计

定理：，其中

$$
\begin{align*}
&\Omega_0:{(x,y)|(x-x_0)2+(y-y_0)2\le a2t_02}\
&\Omega_t:{(x,y)|(x-x_0)2+(y-y_0)2\le a2(t-t_0)2}
\end{align*}

\begin{align*}
E(\Omega_t)=\int_{\Omega_t}u_t2+a2(u_x2+u_y2)dxdy
\end{align*}
$$

证明：即证

由于

$$
\begin{align*}
\frac{d}{dt}E(\Omega_t)&=\frac{d}{dt}\int_{(x-x_0)2+(y-y_0)2\le a2(t-t_0)2}u_t2+a2(u_x2+u_y2)dxdy\
&=\frac{d}{dt}\int_{0}{a(t_0-t)}dr\int_{0}{2\pi r}u_t2+a2(u_x2+u_y2)dxdy\
&=2\int_0{a(t_0-t)}\int_0{2\pi r} u_tu_{tt}+a2(u_xu_{xt}+u_yu_{yt})dsdr-a\int_{0}{2\pi a(t_0-t)}u_t2+a2(u_x2+u_y2)ds\
&=2\int_{\Omega_t}u_t(u_{tt}-a2(u_{xx}+u_{yy}))dxdy+2a2\int_{\Omega_t}\partial_x(u_xu_t)+\partial_y(u_yu_t)dxdy\
&\quad \quad -a\int_{\partial \Omega_t}u_t2+a2(u_x2+u_y2)ds\
&=2a^2\int_{\partial \Omega_t}u_xu_t\cos(x,n)+u_yu_t\cos(y,n)ds-a\int_{\partial \Omega_t}u_t2+a2(u_x2+u_y2)ds\
&=\int_{\partial \Omega_t}-a(u_t2+a2(u_x2+u_y2))+2a^2(u_xu_t\cos(x,n)+u_yu_t\cos(y,n))ds
\end{align*}
$$

由于$\cos2(x,n)+\cos2(y,n)=1u_t2=u_t2\cos2(x,n)+u_t2\cos^2(y,n)$

于是有

$$
\begin{align*}
\frac{dE(\Omega_t)}{dt}=(-a)\int_{\partial \Omega_t}\Big(u_t\cos(x,n)-au_x\Big)2+\Big(u_t\cos(y,n)-au_y\Big)2ds\le 0
\end{align*}
$$

二维波动方程柯西问题的稳定性
